//! Direct port of `agent/core/categories.py`. Field-for-field, entry-for-entry
//! parity with the Python source is the point of this module — see
//! `tests/golden_fixture_tests.rs`, which replays fixtures generated by
//! running the REAL, unmodified Python code
//! (`artifacts/desktop-client/AG-006/generate_golden_fixtures.py`), not a
//! hand-guessed re-derivation of what it probably does.

